import { Badge } from '@/registry/default/ui/badge';
import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader, CardTitle } from '@/registry/default/ui/card';
import { Phone, Mail, Globe, Truck, MapPin } from 'lucide-react';

const supplierData = {
  companyName: 'TechFlow Solutions',
  phone: '+(44)-892-1547',
  email: 'orders@techflow.co.uk',
  website: 'techflow.co.uk',
  address: {
    city: 'Manchester',
    state: 'England',
    zipCode: 'M1 4BT',
    country: 'United Kingdom'
  },
  shippingCarriers: [
    {
      name: 'DHL',
      logo: 'https://logos-world.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/DHL-Logo.png'
    },
    {
      name: 'UPS',
      logo: 'https://logos-world.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/UPS-Logo.png'
    },
    {
      name: 'Royal Mail',
      logo: 'https://logos-world.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Royal-Mail-Logo.png'
    }
  ]
};

export default function ListCard1() {
  return (
    <div className="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-6 lg:p-8">
      <Card className="w-full md:w-[500px]">
        <CardHeader className="border-0 pt-6 pb-5">
          <CardTitle className="text-lg font-semibold">Supplier Details</CardTitle>
        </CardHeader>
        <CardContent className="space-y-5">
          {/* Phone Number */}
          <div className="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div className="flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5">
              <Phone className="size-4 text-muted-foreground" />
            </div>
            <div className="flex items-center justify-between flex-1">
              <span className="text-sm text-muted-foreground font-medium">Phone Number</span>
              <Badge variant="outline" className="bg-blue-50 border-blue-200 text-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-50">
                {supplierData.phone}
              </Badge>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Email */}
          <div className="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div className="flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5">
              <Mail className="size-4 text-muted-foreground" />
            </div>
            <div className="flex items-center justify-between flex-1">
              <span className="text-sm text-muted-foreground font-medium">Email</span>
              <Badge variant="outline" className="bg-blue-50 border-blue-200 text-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-50">
                {supplierData.email}
              </Badge>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Website */}
          <div className="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div className="flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5">
              <Globe className="size-4 text-muted-foreground" />
            </div>
            <div className="flex items-center justify-between flex-1">
              <span className="text-sm text-muted-foreground font-medium">Website</span>
              <Badge variant="outline" className="bg-blue-50 border-blue-200 text-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-50">
                {supplierData.website}
              </Badge>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Shipping Carriers */}
          <div className="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div className="flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5">
              <Truck className="size-4 text-muted-foreground" />
            </div>
            <div className="flex items-center justify-between flex-1">
              <span className="text-sm text-muted-foreground font-medium">Shipping Carrier</span>
              <div className="flex items-center gap-2">
                {supplierData.shippingCarriers.map((carrier, index) => (
                  <div key={index} className="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-6 bg-white border rounded overflow-hidden">
                    <img 
                      src={carrier.logo} 
                      alt={carrier.name}
                      className="h-4 w-auto object-contain"
                      onError={(e) => {
                        const target = e.target as HTMLImageElement;
                        target.style.display = 'none';
                      }}
                    />
                  </div>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Address */}
          <div className="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div className="flex items-center justify-center w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
              <MapPin className="size-4 text-muted-foreground" />
            </div>
            <div className="flex items-start justify-between flex-1">
              <span className="text-sm text-muted-foreground font-medium">Address</span>
              <div className="text-right">
                <div className="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">
                  {supplierData.address.city}, {supplierData.address.state}
                </div>
                <div className="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">
                  {supplierData.address.zipCode} {supplierData.address.country}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </CardContent>
      </Card>
    </div>
  );
}
